China’s western border.

171
00:07:58,920 --> 00:08:02,670
And then there’s the fact that most of Asia’s
rivers start in Tibet.

172
00:08:02,670 --> 00:08:05,800
That gives whoever controls Tibet tremendous
power over

173
00:08:05,800 --> 00:08:08,090
